\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ohio-born star then returned to Cleveland in 2014, guiding the team to their maiden NBA Championship in 2016 and in 2018.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2266, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"score\": 0.9999774616806161, \"rank\": 2.2451717703864013e-05, \"text\": \"Cleveland\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Ohio-born star\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"their maiden NBA Championship\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then switched sides again, this time joining the Los Angeles Lakers, where he won a fifth NBA title in 2020, the franchise's 17th in total.\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.909975057514453e-49, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Lakers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\"}, {\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3102374208338984e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sides\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the franchise's 17th\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His achievements off the court are equal